Grimlock folds his arms into a menacing position, and glares down at the
other robots. "Well, what our first move?" He asks gruffly.

Strafe ran towards the storage room, leaving his team-mates out (they
might be out forever with the rate rAuq posts with them). Seeing most of
the higher officers, minus Scattershot, Strafe stood to attention,
making a slight clearing noise in his throat to get noticed. 


______________________________________________________________________

Outside of the base, a few miles away, a roaring engine could be heard,
as a small red car raced over the dry terrain, his tires squeeling
against the ground. "Almost there Torca." He shouted.
